claim.claim-text:
1. An arc chamber for low-voltage circuit breakers, characterized in that it comprises: 
multiple substantially U-shaped metallic plates (30); 
an enclosure (40) made of insulating material which is substantially shaped like a parallelepiped and comprises two side walls (41, 42), a bottom wall (43), a top wall (44) and a rear wall (46), said side walls (41, 42) having, on the inside, multiple mutually opposite slots (47) for the insertion of said metal plates (30), the bottom and top walls (43, 44) each having at least one opening (48, 49), said enclosure (40) being open at the front.
